text: Le Dévoluy is a commune in the Hautes-Alpes department. The municipality was created on 1 January 2013 by combining Agnières-en-Dévoluy, La Cluse, Saint- Disdier and Saint-Étienne-en-Dévoluy. == References == Category:2013 establishments in France Category:Communes in Hautes-Alpes
title: Le Dévoluy
